## Static Files (Public Directory)

Files in `public/` are served directly without processing.

```
public/
├── 404.html              # Custom 404 page
├── 422.html              # Unprocessable entity page
├── 500.html              # Server error page
├── robots.txt            # Search engine instructions
├── sitemap.xml           # Site map
└── uploads/              # User-uploaded files (via ActiveStorage)
```

### robots.txt

```
# public/robots.txt

User-agent: *
Disallow: /admin/
Disallow: /api/
Allow: /

Sitemap: https://example.com/sitemap.xml
```

